呐喊。2018年2月，出演2018年央视春晚小品《学车》。","name":"蔡明","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Cai Ming","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"蔡明","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Цай Мин","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"蔡明，回族，著名錶演藝術家，國家一級演員。中國著名小品、影視演員。她幼年曾是中央電視台銀河少年合唱團的演員。初中畢業後，蔡明進入了北影廠演員劇團。\n\n1973 年，被導演謝鐵驪選中在影片《海霞》飾演童年海霞。1980 年，參演電影《戴手銬的旅客》。1990 年蔡明的第一個小品是與陳佩斯、朱時茂合演的《普拉尼特的長髮》，在北京電視台亮相。1991 年中央電視台春節聯歡晚會上，蔡明與鞏漢林合作表演了小品《陌生人》。2000 年，在電視劇《閒人馬大姐》中飾演馬大姐，獲得《中國大眾電視》老百姓最喜愛影視明星等榮譽稱號。1991 年至 2017 年，蔡明共計有 26 次登上央視春晚表演小品；2012 年至 2014 年，蔡明已聯續 3 次登上央視元宵晚會演唱歌曲。\n\n2014 年，蔡明擔任《出彩中國人》評委，為實現中國夢的中華兒女搖旗吶喊。2018 年 2 月，出演 2018 年央視春晚小品《學車》。","name":"蔡明","primary":false}}]}},"tv_313711_keywords":{"at":1774722345315,"data":{"id":313711,"results":[]}},"person_1599854_translations":{"at":1774722348901,"data":{"id":1599854,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Zhang Tian'ai, also known by her English name Crystal Zhang, is a Chinese actress and model. She is best known for her breakout role in the 2015 hit web-drama \"Go Princess Go\". Following her fame with \"Go Princess Go\", Zhang was succeedingly cast in bigger projects. In 2016, she starred in the romance film \"I Belonged to You\" alongside Deng Chao. The film was a commercial success and earned more than 800 million yuan ($118 million USD) at the box office.","name":"Zhang Tian'ai","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"　　中国内地女演员。2009年，首次触电拍摄微电影《落樱》。2014年出演抗战剧《二炮手》，凭借“凌织羽”一角获得第2届横店影视文荣奖最佳女配角奖。2015年，主演古装剧《太子妃升职记》，因饰演太子妃张芃芃受到更多关注。2016年9月29日，主演的首部电影《从你的全世界路过》上映，同年成为联想、哈根达斯、巴黎欧莱雅等品牌代言人。主演古装玄幻剧《武动乾坤》。2017年，主演古装奇幻电影《鲛珠传》。","name":"张天爱","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Trương Thiên Ái","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"張天愛","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"中國內地女演員。2009 年，首次觸電拍攝微電影《落櫻》。2014 年出演抗戰劇《二炮手》，憑藉“淩織羽”一角獲得第 2 屆橫店影視文榮獎最佳女配角獎。2015 年，主演古裝劇《太子妃升職記》，因飾演太子妃張芃芃受到更多關注。2016 年 9 月 29 日，主演的首部電影《從你的全世界路過》上映，同年成為聯想、哈根達斯、巴黎歐萊雅等品牌代言人。主演古裝玄幻劇《武動乾坤》。2017 年，主演古裝奇幻電影《鮫珠傳》。","name":"張天愛","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Чжан Тянь Ай","primary":false}}]}},"person_1349626_translations":{"at":1774722353799,"data":{"id":1349626,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"Elijah Canlas es un actor filipino. Estaba estudiando artes teatrales en la Escuela Superior de Arte de Filipinas cuando hizo su primera película \"Sundalong Kanin\" (2014). Terminó la escuela secundaria en MINT College. Actualmente estudia en la Universidad de Filipinas, Manila, mientras realiza películas y series de manera continua.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Elijah Luiz Madiclum Canlas is a Filipino television, film and theater actor and commercial model. His lead and title role in the film Kalel, 15 paved the way for more acting opportunities in his career. This film also bagged its director, Jun Robles Lana, the best director award at the Tallinn International Film Festival in Estonia, and Elijah's first Best Actor award at the 17th Asian Film Festival held in Rome, Italy. In May 2020, he was cast as one of the main actors in the YouTube series, Gameboys. Produced by The IdeaFirst Company, it is a boys love (BL) series in the Philippines that tackles the story of two young men who find each other online amid the COVID-19 pandemic. Second of three siblings, he is fondly called Jelo by his older brother Jerom, and younger brother, JM. The Canlas brothers are all actors who played various roles in film, theater and television. With their mother being a theater actress in Bacolod, they were exposed to theater at a very young age.","name":"Elijah Canlas","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"菲律宾演员。\n\n他目前在马尼拉菲律宾大学攻读菲律宾艺术学士学位，同时不断追求自己的表演生涯。\n\n2014年，他作为电影《圣达隆·卡宁[》中的四个主要角色之一出道。\n\n2020年8月5日，他凭借电影《卡莱尔》在意大利罗马举行第17届亚洲电影节上获得了自己的第一个最佳男演员奖。","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"PH","iso_639_1":"tl","name":"","english_name":"Tagalog","data":{"biography":"","name":"Elijah Canlas","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"菲律賓演員。\n\n他目前在馬尼拉菲律賓大學攻讀菲律賓藝術學士學位，同時不斷追求自己的表演生涯。\n\n2014 年，他作為電影《聖達隆·卡寧[》中的四個主要角色之一齣道。\n\n2020 年 8 月 5 日，他憑藉電影《卡萊爾》在義大利羅馬舉行第 17 屆亞洲電影節上獲得了自己的第一個最佳男演員獎。","name":"","primary":false}}]}},"tv_285739_credits":{"at":1774722354997,"data":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":3293,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Rachel Weisz","original_name":"Rachel Weisz","popularity":5.1882,"profile_path":"/9tfHL5tholha1YF6bSKt422ETPM.jpg","character":"M","credit_id":"67c740a0784c571b4fac916d","order":0},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":3477880,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Leo Woodall","original_name":"Leo Woodall","popularity":3.2987,"profile_path":"/bGRskiP5N2OBP1wcJRVhiYX241.jpg","character":"Vladimir","credit_id":"686ca8002fd12326827032e8","order":1},{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":1202689,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"